<lb n="0423b10" ed="T"/><note n="0423033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">散＋（也）【甲】</note><note n="0423033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">散【大】，散也【甲】</note><app n="0423033"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">散也</rdg></app>。一切曜不吉祥，誦此真言成能吉祥。</p>
<lb n="0423b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0423b1101">北斗七星真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0423b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0423b1201" cb:type="dharani">唵颯跢曩而<note place="inline">齒</note>曩野伴惹<note n="0423034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＋（惹）【甲】</note><note n="0423034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密【大】，密惹【甲】</note><app n="0423034"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">密惹</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">二合</note>染普他摩
<lb n="0423b13" ed="T"/>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>弭曩<note place="inline">名位</note><app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>訖山婆嚩都<app type="star" corresp="#0422032"><lem wit="【大】">莎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">娑嚩</rdg></app><note n="0423035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀引【甲】</note><note n="0423035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，賀引【甲】</note><app n="0423035"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0423b1401">若羅<note n="0423036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">睺＝曜【甲】</note><note n="0423036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">睺【大】，曜【甲】</note><app n="0423036"><lem wit="【大】">睺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曜</rdg></app>、計都暗行人本命星宮，須誦此北斗
<lb n="0423b15" ed="T"/>真言。一切如來說，破一切宿曜<note n="0423037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔障〕－【甲】</note><note n="0423037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">障【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0423037"><lem wit="【大】">障</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>吉祥真
<lb n="0423b16" ed="T"/>言曰：</p>
<lb n="0423b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0423b1701" cb:type="dharani">唵薩羅嚩諾剎怛<app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>三<note n="0423038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【甲】</note><note n="0423038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩【大】，麼【甲】</note><app n="0423038"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麼</rdg></app>曳室<app type="star" corresp="#0423003"><lem wit="【大】">里</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">哩</rdg></app>曳扇
<lb n="0423b18" ed="T"/>底迦<note n="0423039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔俱〕－【甲】</note><note n="0423039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俱【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0423039"><lem wit="【大】">俱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚕娑嚩<note n="0423040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝二合賀引【甲】</note><note n="0423040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】，二合賀引【甲】</note><app n="0423040"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二合賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0423b1901">《金剛<note n="0423041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宿＝大【甲】</note><note n="0423041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宿【大】，大【甲】</note><app n="0423041"><lem wit="【大】">宿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>成就經．吉祥成就品》<note n="0423042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝云【甲】</note><note n="0423042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰【大】，云【甲】</note><app n="0423042"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">云</rdg></app>：「我今宣說
<lb n="0423b20" ed="T"/>世間成就<note n="0423043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（最）＋妙【甲】</note><note n="0423043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙【大】，最妙【甲】</note><app n="0423043"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">最妙</rdg></app>祕法。如是諸曜運行虛空，若一
<lb n="0423b21" ed="T"/>若二三四五等，臨入眾生命宿、對衝宿、遷移
<lb n="0423b22" ed="T"/>宿、大殺<note n="0423044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（宿）＋業【甲】</note><note n="0423044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">業【大】，宿業【甲】</note><app n="0423044"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">宿業</rdg></app>宿、安宿、薄相宿、奴婢宿作諸厄害；
<lb n="0423b23" ed="T"/>四大惡曜，所謂火曜、土曜、羅睺、計都最重眾
<lb n="0423b24" ed="T"/>生，是時修諸福業、廣施<note n="0423045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁慈＝慈仁【甲】</note><note n="0423045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仁慈【大】，慈仁【甲】</note><app n="0423045"><lem wit="【大】">仁慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慈仁</rdg></app>，或依文殊八字
<lb n="0423b25" ed="T"/>真言，<note n="0423046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（又）【甲】</note><note n="0423046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或【大】，或又【甲】</note><app n="0423046"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">或又</rdg></app>依熾盛光佛頂，或依被葉衣觀音，
<lb n="0423b26" ed="T"/>或依一字王佛頂，立<note n="0423047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火【甲】</note><note n="0423047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，火【甲】</note><app n="0423047"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">火</rdg></app>息災護摩壇場，各
<lb n="0423b27" ed="T"/>依本法念誦供養，一切災難自然消滅。作成
<lb n="0423b28" ed="T"/>就法，於心宿直日、柳宿直日、昴宿直日、牛宿直
<lb n="0423b29" ed="T"/>日，不簡日月吉凶，但於此宿直日，於一日之
<pb n="0423c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1304.0423c"/>
<lb n="0423c01" ed="T"/>中不食，念誦滿一千八<note n="0423048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十〕－【甲】</note><note n="0423048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0423048"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>遍，所有心願應時
<lb n="0423c02" ed="T"/>便<note n="0423049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渴＝得【甲】</note><note n="0423049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渴【大】，得【甲】</note><app n="0423049"><lem wit="【大】">渴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">得</rdg></app>大悉地。若厄難時，於本生日最<note n="0423050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋相【甲】</note><note n="0423050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，為相【甲】</note><app n="0423050"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為相</rdg></app>應。
<lb n="0423c03" ed="T"/>若作木曜成就法者，月十六日最為相應。若
<lb n="0423c04" ed="T"/>作火曜成<note n="0423051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">就＝熟【甲】＊</note><note n="0423051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">就【大】＊，熟【甲】＊</note><app n="0423051"><lem wit="【大】">就</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">熟</rdg></app>法者，即彼直日最為相應。若作
<lb n="0423c05" ed="T"/>土曜成<app type="star" corresp="#0423051"><lem wit="【大】">就</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">熟</rdg></app>法者，每月七日最為相應。若作金
<lb n="0423c06" ed="T"/>曜成就法者，隨所見方平<note n="0423052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旦＋（最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦）【甲】</note><note n="0423052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">旦【大】，旦最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦【甲】</note><app n="0423052"><lem wit="【大】">旦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">旦最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦</rdg></app><note n="0423053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">最為相應＝為勝【甲】</note><note n="0423053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">最為相應【大】，為勝【甲】</note><app n="0423053"><lem wit="【大】">最為相應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為勝</rdg></app>。若
<lb n="0423c07" ed="T"/>作水曜成就法者，依水曜直日而作成就。若
<lb n="0423c08" ed="T"/>作羅睺、計都法者，依本生<note n="0423054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（星）＋日【甲】</note><note n="0423054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，星日【甲】</note><app n="0423054"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">星日</rdg></app>以為相應。若復
<lb n="0423c09" ed="T"/>供養本<note n="0423055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝星【甲】</note><note n="0423055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生【大】，星【甲】</note><app n="0423055"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">星</rdg></app>宿者，於本生年<note n="0423056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月＝日【甲】</note><note n="0423056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月【大】，日【甲】</note><app n="0423056"><lem wit="【大】">月</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">日</rdg></app>、若本生日而
<lb n="0423c10" ed="T"/>可取成就。若惡宿生，每月供養、若三<note n="0423057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＋（五日）【甲】</note><note n="0423057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，日五日【甲】</note><app n="0423057"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">日五日</rdg></app>七日
<lb n="0423c11" ed="T"/>供<note n="0423058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養＋（惡曜）【甲】</note><note n="0423058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">養【大】，養惡曜【甲】</note><app n="0423058"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">養惡曜</rdg></app>，直轉成吉祥直。祕勿令知<note n="0423059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俗＋（人）【甲】</note><note n="0423059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俗【大】，俗人【甲】</note><app n="0423059"><lem wit="【大】">俗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俗人</rdg></app>也。」<note n="0423060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書云康元二年二月晦日於覺洞院中寫之了觀尊二十二</note></p>
<lb n="0423c12" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>宿曜儀軌一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
